
CRD	custom resource defnition
CNI	container network interface
CRI	container runtime interface
CSI	container storage interface
IPAM	ip address management
SMI	service mesh interface

k8s/kubernetes: A platform for managing containerized workloads that facilitates declarative config and automation

pod:    A group of containers with shared storage and network resources and a specification for how to run the containers.
label:  key-value pair defined by the user associated with a pod
daemon-set: a collection of pods which are assigned to every node of the cluster

workload:          an application running in k8s
workload resource: an object that manages a workload
deployment:        a workload resource in which every pod is replaceable
statefulSet:
